{{Infobox television |show_name = Dragon Age: Redemption |image = Dragon Age - Redemption (logo).png |genre = |creator = [[Felicia Day]] |writer = Felicia Day |director = Peter Winther |starring = Felicia Day |composer = |country = United States |language = English |num_seasons = 1 |num_episodes = 6 ([[#List of episodes|List of episodes]]) |list_episodes = |producer = |distributor = |location = |cinematography = John Bartley |runtime = |network = |first_aired = October 10, 2011 |last_aired = |website = }} '''''Dragon Age: Redemption''''' is a six-part [[webseries]] based on the [[BioWare]] [[Dragon Age|video game series of the same name]]. It is created by and stars [[Felicia Day]], creator and star of the webseries ''[[The Guild (web series)|The Guild]]''.<ref name="FeliciaDayDragonAge">{{cite web|url=http://feliciaday.com/blog/dragon-age-redemption|title=Felicia Day Blog Archive: Dragon Age: Redemption|author=Felicia Day|publisher=|accessdate=17 November 2014}}</ref> Day is playing Tallis, an Elven assassin.<ref name="FeliciaDayDragonAge" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/tech/gaming/2011-02-15-felicia15_ST_N.htm|title=Felicia Day breathes fire into 'Dragon Age' series|work=USATODAY.COM|accessdate=17 November 2014}}</ref> Filming began in early January 2011 and Day has enlisted the help of many prior [[Hollywood]] acquaintances.
The web series premiered on October 10, 2011.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/tv/la-ca-felicia-day-20110925,0,2638727.story?track=icymi|title=Comic-Con icon Felicia Day, LA Times|work=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=17 November 2014}}</ref>
